Gen0: New guests who might leave soon (short-lived objects).
Gen1: Guests whoâ€™ve stayed for a bit.
Gen2: Long-term guests who arenâ€™t leaving anytime soon.
Why? Most guests leave quickly, so it makes sense to focus on clearing out the new ones more often! ğŸšª

